sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS via service-ca
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PVC as PVC Storage<br/>Filesystem
    participant DB as Database (optional)<br/>Varies/TCP JDBC TLS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus UWM<br/>HTTP scrape
    participant InferenceService as KServe InferenceService<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    %% Flow 1: Model Monitoring Setup
    rect rgb(200, 220, 240)
        Note over User,InferenceService: Flow 1: Model Monitoring and Metrics Collection
        User->>TrustyAI: Create TrustyAIService CR<br/>via kubectl/oc
        Note over TrustyAI: Operator reconciles<br/>and creates resources
        TrustyAI->>InferenceService: Watch InferenceService CR<br/>K8s API
        TrustyAI->>InferenceService: Patch Deployment<br/>Inject payload processor
        InferenceService->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Inference data
        TrustyAI->>PVC: Store model data<br/>Filesystem write
        alt Database mode enabled
            TrustyAI->>DB: JDBC INSERT<br/>Varies/TCP TLS (optional)<br/>Username/Password
        end
        Prometheus->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir<br/>Prometheus format
    end

    %% Flow 2: User Access via Route
    rect rgb(240, 220, 200)
        Note over User,TrustyAI: Flow 2: Authenticated User Access
        User->>Route: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (optional)
        Route->>OAuth: Forward (Reencrypt)<br/>443→8443/TCP HTTPS
        OAuth->>OAuth: Validate Token<br/>OpenShift TokenReview
        OAuth->>TrustyAI: Proxy request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Internal TLS
        TrustyAI-->>OAuth: Response (metrics/data)
        OAuth-->>Route: HTTPS Response
        Route-->>User: HTTPS Response
    end

    %% Flow 3: LMEvalJob Execution
    rect rgb(220, 240, 220)
        Note over User,DB: Flow 3: LMEvalJob Execution
        User->>TrustyAI: Create LMEvalJob CR<br/>via kubectl/oc
        Note over TrustyAI: Operator creates Kueue Workload
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Create LMES Driver Pod<br/>Job/Batch
        Note over TrustyAI: LMES Driver executes<br/>lm-eval-harness
        TrustyAI->>PVC: Write evaluation results<br/>Filesystem
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Update LMEvalJob Status<br/>K8s CRD Status
    end
